block.p: Diane Catherine Clehane and James Joseph Donovan Jr. were married on Friday by the Rev. Louis J. Mazza at the Immaculate Conception Roman Catholic Church in Sleepy Hollow, N.Y.

Ms. Clehane, 38, who will keep her name, is a freelance entertainment reporter and contributing editor to TV Guide magazine. She received a bachelor's degree cum laude in journalism and sociology from the University of Massachusetts at Amherst. She is the daughter of Charles Clehane of East Stroudsburg, Pa., and the late Rita Clehane.

Mr. Donovan, 41, is a senior underwriter in Armonk, N.Y., for Swiss Re, a reinsurance company. He received bachelor's and M.B.A. degrees from Fordham University. He is a son of Rose Ann Donovan of Bay Shore, N.Y., and the late Mr. Donovan Sr.
